{"data":[{"id":564312069,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":307595822,"title":"高中生对哥德巴赫猜想的证明有哪些错误？","question_type":"normal","created":1546272354,"updated_time":1546301579,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"11dc7060fa61f96fd0c0ef74f6931463","url_token":"","name":"知乎用户","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":4,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":true},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/564312069","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546352037,"updated_time":1546352037,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":0,"comment_count":1,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e利益无关：吃瓜的高三群众\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e哥德巴赫猜想什么的我也不会证，关于这个神仙证明我也没什么可说的......\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不过我要科普一下......事实上素数可以有负的......\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e以下所有的概念均在整环\u003c/b\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=S%3D%28S%2C%2B%2C%5Ctimes%29\" alt=\"S=(S,+,\\times)\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e中讨论。\u003c/b\u003e事实上初等数论讨论的就是 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=S%3D%5Cmathbb%7BZ%7D\" alt=\"S=\\mathbb{Z}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 的情形。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e记 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=S+\" alt=\"S \" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 中的零元为 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=0\" alt=\"0\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ，幺元素为 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cepsilon\" alt=\"\\epsilon\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ，这两个概念在 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cmathbb%7BZ%7D\" alt=\"\\mathbb{Z}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 中分别对应 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=0\" alt=\"0\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 和 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cpm+1\" alt=\"\\pm 1\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我们先来几个整除理论中最基本的定义：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cblockquote\u003e\u003cb\u003e相伴数：\u003c/b\u003e设 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=a%2Cb%5Cin+S\" alt=\"a,b\\in S\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e，若存在幺元素 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cepsilon\" alt=\"\\epsilon\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 使得 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=a%3D%5Cepsilon%5Ctimes+b\" alt=\"a=\\epsilon\\times b\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ，则称 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=a\" alt=\"a\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 与 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=b\" alt=\"b\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 相伴。后文中若没有特别指出，所有的“相等”与“不等”均指在相伴意义下。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cb\u003e整除：\u003c/b\u003e设 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=a%2Cb%5Cin+S\" alt=\"a,b\\in S\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ， \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=a%5Cneq+0\" alt=\"a\\neq 0\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ，若 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cexists+p%5Cin+S\" alt=\"\\exists p\\in S\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 使得 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=b%3Da%5Ctimes+p\" alt=\"b=a\\times p\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ，则称 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=b\" alt=\"b\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 被 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=a\" alt=\"a\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 整除，记作 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=a%5Cmid+b\" alt=\"a\\mid b\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 。此时称 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=a\" alt=\"a\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 是 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=b\" alt=\"b\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 的\u003cb\u003e约数\u003c/b\u003e。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cb\u003e素数：\u003c/b\u003e设 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=n%5Cin+S\" alt=\"n\\in S\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 且满足 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=n%5Cneq+0\" alt=\"n\\neq 0\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 且 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=n\" alt=\"n\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 在整环中不是幺元素， \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=a%2Cb%5Cin+S\" alt=\"a,b\\in S\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ，若 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=p%5Cmid+ab%5CLeftrightarrow+p%5Cmid+a+%5Cvee+p%5Cmid+b\" alt=\"p\\mid ab\\Leftrightarrow p\\mid a \\vee p\\mid b\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ，则称 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=n\" alt=\"n\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 为素数。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cb\u003e不可约数：\u003c/b\u003e设 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=n%5Cin+S\" alt=\"n\\in S\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 且满足 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=n%5Cneq+0\" alt=\"n\\neq 0\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 且 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=n\" alt=\"n\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 在整环中不是幺元素，若 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=n\" alt=\"n\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 没有与 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cepsilon\" alt=\"\\epsilon\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 和自身不等的约数，则称其为不可约数。\u003c/blockquote\u003e\u003cp\u003e事实上，由于整环 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%28%5Cmathbb%7BZ%7D%2C%2B%2C%5Ctimes%29\" alt=\"(\\mathbb{Z},+,\\times)\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 是一个欧几里得整环，所以所有的素数都是不可约数，反之亦然。\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e显然，对于任何正素数的相反数，可以证明它既符合素数的定义又符合不可约数的定义。因此负素数是存在的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e中学数学竞赛大纲内的初等数论，既然会用到负数，就理应承认负素数的存在。只不过在中学竞赛中讨论负素数只会增加无谓的讨论细节，因此约定只讨论正的素数。\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e可能有的人会说我们只在整环 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=N%3D%28%5Cmathbb%7BN%7D%2C%2B%2C%5Ctimes%29\" alt=\"N=(\\mathbb{N},+,\\times)\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 中讨论不就没有负素数了吗。请注意自然数的加法和乘法并不能构成一个环，更别说整环了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当然要是你能忍受每次写完整除式 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=n%5Cmid+a%5E2-4a%2B3\" alt=\"n\\mid a^2-4a+3\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 后必须注明 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=a%5Cin%5Cmathbb%7BN%7D%5Cwedge+a%5Cnot%5Cin+%281%2C3%29\" alt=\"a\\in\\mathbb{N}\\wedge a\\not\\in (1,3)\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 我也没意见。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"利益无关：吃瓜的高三群众哥德巴赫猜想什么的我也不会证，关于这个神仙证明我也没什么可说的......不过我要科普一下......事实上素数可以有负的......\u003cb\u003e以下所有的概念均在整环\u003c/b\u003e S=(S,+,\\times)\u003cb\u003e中讨论。\u003c/b\u003e事实上初等数论讨论的就是 S=\\mathbb{Z} 的情形。记 S 中…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=373\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%